Daily Trust newspaper has won Silver Award in the Website of the Year Award. The Nigerian Online Merit Award gave Daily Trust the award in an event organized to mark this year's Website of the Year Award in Lagos. The management in a statement described the award as a feat of hard work, commitment and dedication of its staff in contributing their quota towards achieving the company's goal. “This is a remarkable achievement coming from the stable of this company as a mark of distinction in our service delivery process. “It is a feat of hard work, commitment and dedication from all and sundry in contributing their quota towards achieving the company's goal" the statement read. The management, however, congratulated the staff for their contribution in uplifting the company to enviable height.